lass="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_21us" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/NancyLebovitz/">NancyLebovitz</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">25 May 2010 11:15:25AM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_21us'>3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_21us'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_21us')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_21us" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
