_t1_20u9'>4 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_20u9'] = ['3 points', '4 points', '5 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_20u9')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_20u9" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
