<p><a href="http://gse.buffalo.edu/fas/bromley/ccs/part5.htm" rel="nofollow">Jane Jacobs</a></p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1ycu"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_1ycu" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1ycu')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_1ycu" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1ycu')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_1ycu" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/26y/rationality_quotes_may_2010/1ycu?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_1ycu" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_1ycu')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_1ycu class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1ycu" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_1ycu" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_1ycu" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1yee" class="morechildren" ><div id="pre_t1_1yee" class="parent"></div><div id="entry_t1_1yee" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1yee" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'></div><div id="display_t1_1yee" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"></div><div id="body_t1_1yee" class="comment-content"><span class="morecomments"><a style="font-size: smaller; font-weight: bold" id="more_t1_1yee" href="javascript:void()" onclick="return morechildren(this, 't3_26y', ['1yee'], 1)">load more comments<span class="gray">&nbsp;(3 replies)</span></a></span></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1yee"></div><div class="comment-links"></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1yee" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1yce" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1yce" class="parent"><a name="1yce" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1yce" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1yce" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1yce" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/RolfAndreassen/">RolfAndreassen</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">02 May 2010 07:23:07PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " >5 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1yce'] = ['4 points', '5 points', '6 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1yce')">[+] (2 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1yce" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1yce" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/RolfAndreassen/">RolfAndreassen</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">02 May 2010 07:23:07PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1yce'>5 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1yce'] = ['4 points', '5 points', '6 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1yce')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1yce" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>He drew a deep breath, closed his eyes, drew old lessons to his mind. “What is, is. No loss is made better by dwelling on it; no pain is cured by the mind’s eye regarding it. Accept the casualties. Assess your capabilities. Continue the mission.” The recitation made him feel a little better; a cold clarity came to him.</p>
</blockquote>

<p><a href="http://ynglingasaga.wordpress.com/2009/11/27/there-will-be-war-little-black-bottles/" rel="nofollow">And Rumours of War</a>, time-travel story on the Ynglinga Saga blog.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1yce"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_1yce" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1yce')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_1yce" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1yce')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_1yce" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/26y/rationality_quotes_may_2010/1yce?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_1yce" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_1yce')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_1yce class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1yce" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_1yce" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_1yce" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1ymt" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1ymt" class="parent"><a name="1ymt" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1ymt" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1ymt" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1ymt" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/gwern/">gwern</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 May 2010 12:59:19PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " >1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1ymt'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1ymt')">[+] (1 child)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1ymt" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1ymt" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/gwern/">gwern</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 May 2010 12:59:19PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1ymt'>1 point</span><s